---
title: North African Chickpea & Tomato Stew with Currant Couscous & Mint Yoghurt
description: When we first tried this bright burst of goodness, we all agreed it had that "hug in a bowl" kind of feeling. There's wholesome chickpeas, courgette and carrot, plus a sublime, lightly spiced tomato sauce that soaks into the couscous. Enjoy!
